pysandbox is a Python sandbox.

Blocked functions
=================

Functions:

 * Create a file, write into an existing file

Protection of the sandbox itself:

 * Read function closure


Options
=======

You can specify a white list of allowed path using Sandbox(open_whitelist=<your
list>).


Example
=======

Code:

   with Sandbox():
      ... execute unsafe code here ...


